   <p style="margin-left: 1.2in">
   <font size="+2">
  <FONT color="red"><B>Type</B></FONT> a
  <FONT color="blue"><B><TT>true</TT> or a number</B></FONT> and see
  <FONT color="red"><B>what</B></FONT> is 
   <FONT color="blue"><B>stored</B></FONT> in
  <FONT color="red"><B>computer memory</B></FONT>:
   </font>
   </p>

