 <UL>
 <LI> <FONT color="red"><B>Type input:</B></FONT> 
    (this simulates what the computer will receive)
<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<textarea pattern="[\x00-\xFF]*" autofocus cols=40 style="font-size: 18pt">
</textarea>
<P>
<LI> The  <FONT color="red"><B>computer program</B></FONT> will
   <FONT color="blue"><B>receive</B></FONT> the following:
<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<textarea style="font-size: 18pt" cols=40 pattern="(\s*[01]{8}\s*)*">0100100001100101011100100110010100100000011000100110010100100000011100110110010101100011011100100110010101110100001000000110110101100101011100110111001101100001011001110110010101110011001000010010000100110001</textarea>
